metadata.name: The Summer
metadata.description:
The 21st of June marks the start of Summer in the northern hemisphere.  
This is the season the SensualBody duo started their journey into nude photography in 2019, shooting in a completely natural environment without any sight of human intervention. From that moment, they experimented with nude photography every time they found themselves surrounded by an interesting natural environment. 

This particular shoot was inspired by a breathtaking sunset encountered after one hour of hiking for reaching the incredible Tinnari beach in Sardegna, Italy. The remoteness and natural beauty of the landscapes are an essential part of SensualBody photography.

"The Summer"  is part of the ”Seasons” project. For each season it will be minted a new edition that will grand special access to upcoming projects.


Tinnari, Italy.  
September 12th, 2020.


5304 × 6629 pixels  
sRGB
